b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":798,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Announcing the Next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special!","message":"<div>The next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicks off <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1570773600\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The appearance rates for featured 4\\u2605 and 5\\u2605 dragons will be boosted.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This showcase will be available from <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1570773600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571378340\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured dragons below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Featured Dragons:<\/div><div><div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/db87aac30d4fa6ae320bda89aa694330.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>374<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>121<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>995<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>A hot-blooded dragon whose mastery and<br>knowledge of smithing is matched only by the joy<br>he feels in sharing it with humans. The former<br>coach of the blacksmith sisters\' father, he spends<br>his days honing body and mind in a volcano.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/01acd2bf5c9cc9faf3d5d038afad04732.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Dragon Drop<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDeals flame damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts stun.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Flame) Strength & Critical Damage II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Flame:<br>increases strength by 45% and adds 55% to the<br>modifier applied to critical damage.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a1d927e0ae0003a9463a8fc45ccc6100.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>375<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>120<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>1025<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>A beautiful dragon who watches over love and<br>harvests. Her giant staff, made from an ancient<br>tree, spreads nature\'s blessings far and wide.<br>She is adored by all life and loves it in return\\u2014<br>especially her two feline familiars.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/19c706c3440276a68b516e5597e4e0c32.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Breath of Life<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tRestores HP to all allies, continues healing over<br>the next 20 seconds, and energizes the entire team.<br>Once energized, using any applicable skill resets<br>that adventurer\'s energy level to zero.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/756879fc2f94c1df98ecd39bf3dd90ae2.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) HP +30%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind: <br>increases HP by 30%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png\\"><\/span><span>(Wind) Skill Haste +35%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind: <br>increases skill gauge fill rate by 35%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/e140a6e197564b7e3a13e8d83f607776.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>100<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"hp\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>371<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"atk\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Strength<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>124<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"total\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/a8a2cd128481266e95fd4fbbbac90fbd2.png\\" alt=\\"\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>995<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Dragon Details<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>The singing dragon is finally able to stand<br>on the stage of her dreams\\u2014and with an almost<br>frighteningly beautiful voice, she aims to bring<br>joy to everyone. Her outfit was made by her<br>friends, making her an icon of dragalia.<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<\/div><\/div><div class=\\"skill explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Skills<\/div>\\n\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/77c2ac9b0a7142033bc6402d88c4b32d2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Invigorating Harmony<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases the entire team\'s strength and defense<br>by 20% for 20 seconds, and increases their<br>energy levels by three stages. It is possible to<br>charge this skill\'s gauge by attacking, and use it<br>up to twice during one shapeshift.<br>When an adventurer\'s energy level reaches level five,<br>they will become energized, and their next attack or<br>recovery skill will be upgraded. At this point,<br>using any applicable skill will reset that<br>adventurer\'s energy level to zero.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t<\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Light) Strength +40%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases strength by 40%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f95daa91eaca6e0d41a23320398a9e792.png\\"><\/span><span>Exhilaration<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases shapeshift time for the entire team<br>by 3 seconds. The team\'s shapeshift time<br>can only be increased by a maximum of<br>5 seconds through this ability.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The stats shown here represent each dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div>2. For information about featured dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1570687200,"prev_article_id":"808","next_article_id":"774","image_path":"","update_time":1570520625}}}'